   writeBatch.put(markerKey, EMPTY_BYTES);
{code}
and 2.
{code:title=TestRollingLevelDBTimelineStore.java}
  @Test
  public void testGetEntitiesWithFromTs() throws IOException {
    super.testGetEntitiesWithFromTs();
  }
{code}
is changed to 
{code}
